product.descripcion: Proyector compacto para hogar, streaming, compatible HDMI/USB, parlante integrado.

results.angle_name: Cine en casa accesible: gran pantalla por menos de COP 300k
results.buyer_persona: Hogares jóvenes/parejas que ven series/películas y no quieren invertir en TV grande

ad_copy.title: ¡Cine en casa por menos de COP 300k!
ad_copy.primary_text: Convierte cualquier pared en una pantalla gigante de 100" para tus noches de cine. Disfruta sin gastar de más.
ad_copy.description: Proyecta tus pelis favoritas sin complicaciones. Compra ahora y transforma tu entretenimiento casero.

structure_rules.change_definition: Visual, text, rhythm change every beat

beats.visual: Close-up of person pressing power on the projector in a dark room.
beats.rhythm_editing: Quick punch-in to the hand pressing the button.

beats.visual: Projector casting large image on the wall in a cozy living room.
beats.voiceover: Convierte cualquier pared en una pantalla gigante.
beats.rhythm_editing: Zoom out to show full living room view.

beats.visual: Split-screen: left view with light on, right view with light off.
Hands connecting HDMI input, close-up on ports.
beats.rhythm_editing: Quick cuts focusing on connection plug-ins.

beats.visual: Close-up of speaker area, small sound waves shown as graphics.
beats.voiceover: Incluye parlante para una experiencia completa.
beats.rhythm_editing: Quick zoom in on speaker area.

beats.visual: Text overlay atop footage of the cozy home viewing setup.
beats.rhythm_editing: Text pops up with a bounce effect.

beats.visual: Close-up of projector next to coffee and snacks on table.
beats.voiceover: Haz tuyo este proyector portátil ahora.
beats.rhythm_editing: Slow pan across the setup ending with the projector.
beats.sfx_music: Music ends with a soft fade-out.

production_notes: Begin with a close-up shot to immediately engage the audience.
Use warm, inviting lighting to make the home atmosphere appealing.
Include text overlays that are clear and large enough to read instantly.
Maintain a fast pace with quick cuts to keep the video dynamic and engaging.
Incorporate music that is upbeat and aligns with the upbeat cinematic experience.
Show practical uses of the projector to visualize ease of use.
Emphasize the affordable pricing visually and verbally.
Use a mix of wide, medium, and close-up shots for visual variety.
Ensure that all text is centered and visible, even on small screens.

compliance_notes: Avoid making definitive picture quality claims without quantitative data.
Do not refer to warranty or price as higher than disclosed; keep language conditional.

results.angle_name: Streaming sin cables (Android integrado) + conexiones HDMI/USB
results.buyer_persona: Usuarios que ven Netflix/YouTube y quieren evitar conectar laptop cada vez

ad_copy.title: ¡Streaming sin esfuerzo y sin cables!
ad_copy.primary_text: Transforma tu entretenimiento con nuestro proyector portátil y olvídate de los cables.
ad_copy.description: Proyector compacto con Android integrado. Simple, sin complicaciones.

structure_rules.cadence_rule: 3-3-3 cadence (change visual, text, rhythm every 3 seconds)
structure_rules.change_definition: Change at least two elements (visual, text, rhythm) every 3 seconds

beats.visual: User disconnects a tangle of cables from their TV.
beats.voiceover: Olvida los cables con nuestro proyector.
beats.rhythm_editing: Quick cut to next scene on vocal emphasis.
beats.transition: Jump cut from cables to projector.

beats.visual: Close-up of the proyector turned on, apps loading seamlessly on wall.
beats.voiceover: Accede a apps directo desde el proyector.
beats.transition: Zoom in to app screen display.

beats.visual: Split-screen showing HDMI/USB ports being used with gaming consoles and TV sticks.
beats.sfx_music: Highlight sound effect on HDMI plug-in

beats.visual: User browsing apps fluidly, worry-free expression.
beats.rhythm_editing: Steady rhythm to show smooth functioning.
beats.transition: Fade in to user using remote control.

beats.visual: Vibrant movie scene projected in a cozy living room.
beats.voiceover: Llena tu casa de experiencias increíbles.
beats.rhythm_editing: Dynamic cut to a nighttime movie scene.

beats.visual: Close-up of price tag popping on screen, user excited and thumbs up.
beats.transition: Price flash onto screen with sound sync.

beats.on_screen_text: Compra hoy y cambia tu forma de ver.
beats.visual: Logo and call-to-action button "Compra Ahora" on screen.
beats.voiceover: Adquiere el tuyo hoy y comienza a disfrutar.
beats.rhythm_editing: Closing with logo fade and CTA button pop-up.

production_notes: Use energetic music that fits a modern lifestyle.
Ensure captions are clear for sound-off viewing.
Dynamic and quick transitions to maintain viewer attention.
Lighting should be warm and inviting, especially in living room scenes.
Keep text overlays concise and easy to read.
Use realistic and relatable scenarios to showcase product benefits.
Highlight ease of use with simple, clear visuals.
Apply engaging motion graphics especially during text transitions.
Close-ups on key features to emphasize value proposition.
Focus on seamless integration of product into lifestyle settings.

compliance_notes: Ensure all claims about app functionality and connectivity are accurate and supported by product capabilities.
Do not list unconfirmed warranty details; if mentioned, state 'según disponibilidad'.
Avoid any exaggerated claims about streaming quality beyond what typical user experience would expect.
Text overlays and voiceover content should be aligned to avoid contradictions.

results.angle_name: Portátil y flexible (proyecta en pared o techo, base giratoria 180°)
results.buyer_persona: Estudiantes y usuarios con espacios pequeños que buscan ver series en cama o llevarlo de viaje

ad_copy.title: Proyección flexible, en cualquier lugar
ad_copy.primary_text: Transforma cualquier pared o techo en tu cine personal, lleva entretenimiento a donde vayas.
ad_copy.description: Perfecto para espacio reducido y maratones en la cama.

structure_rules.cadence_rule: Introduce a new element every 3 seconds
structure_rules.change_definition: Change visuals, text, or audio every 3 seconds

beats.on_screen_text: Proyecta en cama, en cualquier lugar.
beats.visual: Close-up of projector going into a backpack.
Medium shot of projector being set on a bed.
beats.voiceover: Este mini proyector es tu solución.

beats.visual: POV shot of projecting a movie onto the ceiling.
Demonstration of base rotation with close-up.
Time-lapse of various travel locations with projector.
beats.voiceover: Ideal para cualquier lugar y momento.

beats.visual: Laughing friends watching a movie on a blanket fort.
Close-up of happy student packing the projector.

production_notes: Use diverse backdrops for different settings.
Lighting should be warm and inviting, mimic home environments.
Text overlays in large, clear fonts for quick reading.
Fast-paced edits to align with energetic background music.
Props include cozy bedding, backpack, and outdoor scenes.
Show happy, relatable faces in a relaxed setting.
End with call-to-action visually aligned with voiceover.
